<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<style>
			html,
			body,
			div,
			span,
			applet,
			object,
			iframe,
			h1,
			h2,
			h3,
			h4,
			h5,
			h6,
			p,
			blockquote,
			pre,
			a,
			abbr,
			acronym,
			address,
			big,
			cite,
			code,
			del,
			dfn,
			em,
			img,
			ins,
			kbd,
			q,
			s,
			samp,
			small,
			strike,
			strong,
			sub,
			sup,
			tt,
			var,
			b,
			u,
			i,
			center,
			dl,
			dt,
			dd,
			ol,
			ul,
			li,
			fieldset,
			form,
			label,
			legend,
			table,
			caption,
			tbody,
			tfoot,
			thead,
			tr,
			th,
			td,
			article,
			aside,
			canvas,
			details,
			embed,
			figure,
			figcaption,
			footer,
			header,
			hgroup,
			menu,
			nav,
			output,
			ruby,
			section,
			summary,
			time,
			mark,
			audio,
			video {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				border: 0;
				font-size: 100%;
				font: inherit;
				vertical-align: baseline;
			}

			/* HTML5 display-role reset for older browsers */
			article,
			aside,
			details,
			figcaption,
			figure,
			footer,
			header,
			hgroup,
			menu,
			nav,
			section {
				display: block;
			}

			body {
				line-height: 1;
			}

			ol,
			ul {
				list-style: none;
			}

			blockquote,
			q {
				quotes: none;
			}

			blockquote:before,
			blockquote:after,
			q:before,
			q:after {
				content: "";
				content: none;
			}

			table {
				border-collapse: collapse;
				border-spacing: 0;
			}

			/*
            * Base
            */
			body {
				color: #222222;
				font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, Verdana, "Nimbus Sans L", sans-serif;
				font-weight: normal;
				height: 100%;
				line-height: normal;
				text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: 3em;
				font-weight: bold;
				line-height: 1.1em;
				margin: 0 0 70px;
				min-height: 80px;
				padding: 0;
				width: 300px;
			}

			strong {
				font-weight: bold;
			}

			.cb {
				clear: both;
				height: 20px;
			}

			.tleft {
				text-align: left !important;
			}

			.tright {
				text-align: right !important;
			}

			.footer {
				position: absolute;
				border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;
				padding: 1em 5px 0;
				margin: 0;
			}

			/*
            * Adress
            */
			.address {
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.address_label {
				color: #555;
				float: left;
				font-size: 1em;
				font-weight: normal;
				margin: 0;
				padding-top: 4px;
				text-align: right;
				width: 105px;
			}
			.address_content {
				border-left: 1px solid #cccccc;
				margin-left: 115px;
				padding: 4px 0 4px 10px;
			}
			.address_content strong {
				display: block;
				font-size: 1.2em;
				padding-bottom: 2px;
			}

			.from {
				position: absolute;
				top: 7px;
				right: 0;
				width: 50%;
			}

			.to {
				float: left;
				width: 50%;
			}

			/*
            * Infos
            */
			.infos {
				float: right;
				width: 50%;
			}
			.infos table {
				width: 100%;
			}
			.infos .label {
				text-align: right;
				width: 105px;
				color: #555;
				font-size: inherit;
				padding: 4px 10px 4px 0;
				min-height: 17px;
				white-space: nowrap;
				vertical-align: top;
			}
			.infos .def {
				border-left: 1px solid #cccccc;
				min-height: 17px;
				padding: 4px 10px;
				vertical-align: top;
			}

			/*
            * Table
            */
			.items {
				border-collapse: collapse;
				margin: 50px 0;
				width: 100%;
			}
			.items tbody tr:nth-child(odd) {
				background-color: #f6f6f6;
			}
			.items th {
				border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;
				border-right: 1px solid #cccccc;
				line-height: 1.1em;
				font-size: 0.9em;
				padding: 10px;
				text-align: left;
				vertical-align: top;
				font-weight: bold;
				color: #000;
			}
			.items td {
				border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;
				border-right: 1px solid #cccccc;
				float: none;
				font-weight: normal;
				padding: 10px;
				text-align: left;
				vertical-align: top;
			}
			.items .total {
				background: transparent !important;
			}
			.items .total td {
				border: none;
			}
			.items .total td.label {
				text-align: right;
			}
			.items .total-first td {
				padding-top: 28px;
			}
			.items .total-big td {
				padding-top: 1.1em;
				font-size: 1.3em;
				font-weight: bold;
			}
		</style>
		<script defer>
			window.addEventListener("afterprint", function (event) {
            window.close()
            })
            window.print()
		</script>
		<title>Facture-{{ website_name }}-{{ transaction.id }}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>
			Facture
		</h1>
		<div class="adress from">
			<div class="address_label">
				De
			</div>
			<div class="address_content">
				{{ company }}
				<br>
				SIRET : {{ siret }}
				<br>
				N° TVA intracommunautaire :
				<br>
				{{ vat }}
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="adress to">
			<div class="address_label tleft">
				Pour
			</div>
			<div class="address_content">
				{% if app.user.invoiceInfo %}
					{{ app.user.invoiceInfo | nl2br }}
				{% else %}
					<strong>{{ transaction.fullName }}</strong>
					{{ transaction.address | nl2br }}<br>
					{{ transaction.postalCode }}
					{{ transaction.city }}<br>
					{{ transaction.country }}
				{% endif %}
			</div>
			<div class="cb"></div>
			<div class="address_label tleft">
				Sujet
			</div>
			<div class="address_content">
				{{ transaction.description }}
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="infos">
			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td class="label">
							Facture n°
						</td>
						<td class="def">
							<strong>{{ website_name }}{{ transaction.createdAt.format('Y') }}-{{ transaction.id }}</strong>
						</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td class="label">
							Emise le
						</td>
						<td class="def">
							{{ transaction.createdAt.format('d/m/Y') }}
						</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
		<div class="cb"></div>
		<table class="items">
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>
						Description
					</th>
					<th class="tright" width="108">
						{% if transaction.tax %}
							Prix HT
						{% else %}
							Prix TTC
						{% endif %}
					</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td>{{ transaction.description }}</td>
					<td class="tright">
						<strong>{{ (transaction.price - transaction.tax) | format_currency('EUR') }}</strong>
					</td>
				</tr>

				{% if transaction.tax %}
					<tr class="total">
						<td class="label">
							Taxe (20.00%)</td>
						<td class="tright">
							<strong>
								{{ transaction.tax | format_currency('EUR') }}
							</strong>
						</td>
					</tr>
				{% endif %}

				<tr class="total total-big">
					<td class="label">Total</td>
					<td class="tright">
						<strong>{{ transaction.price | format_currency('EUR') }}</strong>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
		<div class="cb"></div>
		<div class="footer">
			{{ law }}
			<br>
			Adhérent d’un centre de gestion agrée, acceptant à ce titre les règlements par chèque<br>
			Loi 83-629 du 12/07/83, art. 8 : « L'autorisation administrative ne confère aucun caractère officiel à l'entreprise ou
			aux personnes qui en bénéficient. Elle n'engage en aucune manière la responsabilité des pouvoirs publics.»<br>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
